<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 观点；看法；（观察问题的）视角；透视法：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Studying abroad helps you to gain a global perspective and improve your general competence.
出国留学有助于你获得全球视野，提升综合能力。</p><footer>人教新选必② – 2改</footer></div>

